🔐 Secure Coding Review
📌 Description

This project performs a basic security review of code to find vulnerabilities and improve safety.

🎯 Objectives
Analyze code for security issues
Use static analysis tools
Suggest fixes and best practices
🛠️ Tools
Static analyzers (e.g., Bandit, SonarQube)
Manual code review
✅ Outcome

Identified vulnerabilities and provided recommendations for secure coding.
